        <item>
            <title>Apple 靜靜刪除 iPhone 16 鏡頭「抗反射鏡頭塗層」描述，網民實試相機拍強光仍有鬼影</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/26/iphone-16-anti-reflective-lens-coatng/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=iphone-16-anti-reflective-lens-coatng</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/26/iphone-16-anti-reflective-lens-coatng/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 07:25:02 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 16]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 16 Plus]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 16 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 16 Pro Max]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1265492</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Apple 先前在規格表中標明為 iPhone 16 系列增加了「抗反射鏡頭塗層」，以防止在光線複雜的環境下出現「鬼影」問題，惟現時卻被網民發現 Apple 靜靜地刪除了 iPhone 16 系列的後置鏡頭「抗反射鏡頭塗層」描述。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1265526 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240925at-694x395.png" alt="" width="694" height="395" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240925at-694x395.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240925at-1280x729.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Apple 靜靜地刪除了 iPhone 16 系列的後置鏡頭「抗反射鏡頭塗層」描述（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/hk/iphone/compare/?modelList=iphone-16-pro-max,iphone-16-pro,iphone-15-pro">Apple</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">據 MacRumors 論壇用戶指，Apple 早前曾在 iPhone 16 系列的技術規格中提到「抗反射鏡頭塗層」，但這項描述已從 Apple 官網及 Apple Store 應用程式中被悄然移除。Apple 官網當時曾顯示，iPhone 16 Pro 及 Pro Max 配備 「防反光鏡頭塗層」，而 iPhone16 及 16 Plus 則有「抗反射鏡頭塗層（融合式攝像頭）」。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1265523 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/antireflectivelensis-1-423x580.png" alt="" width="423" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/antireflectivelensis-1-423x580.png 423w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/antireflectivelensis-1.png 656w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 423px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲MacRumors 論壇用戶指原本 Apple 有列明 iPhone 16 系列有「抗反射鏡頭塗層」（Anti-reflective lens coating）（圖片來源：<a href="https://forums.macrumors.com/threads/anti-reflective-lens-coating-gone-from-16-line-ups-tech-spec.2437703/">MacRumors</a>）</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1265522 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/cms_2024092215553443-573x580.jpg" alt="" width="573" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/cms_2024092215553443-573x580.jpg 573w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/cms_2024092215553443.jpg 870w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 573px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Apple 官網曾顯示 iPhone 16 Pro 系列配備 「防反光鏡頭塗層」，iPhone 16 系列則有「抗反射鏡頭塗層（融合式攝像頭）」（圖片來源：<a href="https://longportapp.com/zh-HK/news/214870749">LONGPORT</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">抗反射鏡頭塗層技術是透過減少光線在鏡頭表面反射，從而提升成像清晰度及色彩還原度。但從中國網民實際測試結果來看，iPhone 16 在拍攝強光源或複雜光源環境下的物體時，眩光現象依舊明顯。據新浪科技猜測，Apple 有可能避免宣傳不實而引起爭議。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1265529 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240925at-1-1-694x386.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240925at-1-1-694x386.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240925at-1-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中國網民實際測試結果來看，似乎依舊有鬼影</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://forums.macrumors.com/threads/anti-reflective-lens-coating-gone-from-16-line-ups-tech-spec.2437703/">MacRumors</a>、<a href="https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2024/09/apple-debuts-iphone-16-pro-and-iphone-16-pro-max/">Apple</a>、<a href="https://longportapp.com/zh-HK/news/214870749">LONGPORT</a>、<a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/discovery/2024-09-23/doc-incqawwc2141827.shtml">新浪科技</a>、<a href="https://new.qq.com/rain/a/20240924A03C6900">騰訊網</a>、<a href="https://www.apple.com/hk/iphone/compare/?modelList=iphone-16-pro-max,iphone-16-pro,iphone-15-pro">Apple</a>、<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/794/711.htm">IT 之家</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/20/iphone-16-pro-iphone-16/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】iPhone 16 / 16 Pro   新實體影相按鈕 + 大量新相機鏡頭試相 + 無線充電實試</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/18/iphone16proreview/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iPhone 16 Pro Max 詳細開箱影片，並非只「多了顆掣」</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/10/iphone-16-%e7%b3%bb%e5%88%97-pro-max-%e5%a4%96%e5%aa%92%e4%b8%8a%e6%89%8b%e8%a9%95%e6%b8%ac-%e6%b8%af%e4%ba%ba%e6%9c%80%e6%84%9b-18-%e5%80%8b%e5%8a%9f%e8%83%bd-apple-watch-s10-%e5%8f%8a-airpods-4/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iPhone 16 系列 Pro Max 外媒上手評測，港人最愛 18 個功能</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/26/iphone-16-anti-reflective-lens-coatng/mobile-phone/">Apple 靜靜刪除 iPhone 16 鏡頭「抗反射鏡頭塗層」描述，網民實試相機拍強光仍有鬼影</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
