        <item>
            <title>可捉芒亨魔物的數碼暴龍機　Monster Hunter 20 週年最新聯乘產品</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/26/monster-huntert-20th-x-digimon/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=monster-huntert-20th-x-digimon</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/26/monster-huntert-20th-x-digimon/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 06:45:21 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[monster hunter]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[數碼暴龍]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1265608</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>今年是 Monster Hunter 推出 20 週年，今日（26 日）BANDAI 在日本購物網站 Premium Bandai 推出「數碼暴龍 COLOR 魔物獵人 20 週年紀念版」，即日起在日本開放預購，香港的玩家可能要稍等一陣。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265615" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/459163799_8455793810-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/459163799_8455793810-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/459163799_8455793810.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/459163799_8455793810-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有「雄火龍」和「雷狼龍」兩種配色可選</p><div>為紀念《Monster Hunter》系列 20 週年，BANDAI 推出了「數碼暴龍 COLOR 魔物獵人 20 週年紀念版」，提供「雄火龍」和「雷狼龍」兩種配色，內置彩色螢幕，可隨心更換背景，使用隨附的 USB-C 線即可充電。最重要的是，這款 20 週年紀念版可以和過去全部 COLOR 系列對戰。</div><div></div><div><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265616" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/1000215405_1-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/1000215405_1-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/1000215405_1.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/1000215405_1-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></div><div style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://p-bandai.jp/item/item-1000215405/">P-BANDAI.jp</a></div><div></div><div></div><div>是次推出的 20 週年 COLOR 遊戲機收錄了 36 隻魔物，暫時可見有火龍、雷狼龍、泡狐龍、金獅子、奇怪龍、迅龍、黑蝕龍、轟龍，以及今次原創的火龍暴龍獸及雷狼龍加魯魯獸。另外亦設有火山、沙漠、雪山、塔等背景圖案供用家自由切換。</div><div></div><div><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265610" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460660914_2044866779-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460660914_2044866779-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460660914_2044866779.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460660914_2044866779-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></div><div></div><div style="text-align: center;">▲除了一般魔物，更收錄了亞種，合共全 36 種魔物</div><div></div><div></div><div><div>今次更特地邀請了《數碼暴龍》角色設計擔當渡邊けんじ繪製聯乘魔物：雄火龍結合暴龍獸的「レウスグレイモン（火龍暴龍獸）」及雷狼龍結合加魯魯獸的「ジンオウガルルモン（雷狼龍加魯魯獸）」 ，2 款均為可培育魔物。</div><div></div><div></div></div><div><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265611" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/461148042_1223380178-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/461148042_1223380178-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/461148042_1223380178.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/461148042_1223380178-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></div><div></div><div style="text-align: center;">▲渡邊けんじ全新繪製，原創的火龍暴龍獸及雷狼龍加魯魯獸</div><div></div><p>與過去 COLOR 系列相同，玩家在「冷卻模式」時可暫停飢餓、力量值下降。此外，玩家可備份保存魔物。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265612" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460321421_5449507380-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460321421_5449507380-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460321421_5449507380.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460321421_5449507380-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265613" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/459266790_1573947529-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/459266790_1573947529-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/459266790_1573947529.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/459266790_1573947529-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265614" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/461245075_8277401592-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/461245075_8277401592-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/461245075_8277401592.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/461245075_8277401592-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h2>售價、預訂詳情</h2><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 240px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 48px;"><td style="width: 33.0314%; height: 48px;">名稱</td><td style="width: 66.9686%; height: 48px;">デジタルモンスターCOLOR モンスターハンター 20th Edition<br />
