            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1265627</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>今日東京電玩展（TGS）首日開放傳媒、商業機構率先入場，而在昨晚《人中之龍 8 外傳 Pirates in Hawaii》開發商 SEGA 就搞了一場盛大派對，unwire 現場記者亦有入場觀看，重點當然是「港區女子」獲選者有到現場同傳媒一齊玩！之後到今日 SEGA 亦有在會場內提供遊戲試玩。等我們記者在現場為大家報道。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265651" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1530-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1530-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1530.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265656" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1494-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1494-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1494.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265647" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0720-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0720-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0720.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>SEGA 在昨晚搞了一場「SEGA TGS Pre Party」邀請傳媒、KOL 到場一齊狂歡。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265653" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0759-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0759-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0759.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265650" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0703-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0703-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0703.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>《人中之龍 8 外傳 Pirates in Hawaii》遊戲裡面會出現，早前在審查中突為而出的「港區女子」的其中 3 位也有登場。賽車女郎霧島聖子、Coser 澁谷果歩、遊戲直播主 Misoshiru 有到現場，大曬肌肉。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1265648" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0686-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="450" height="800" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0686-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0686-rotated.jpg 506w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 450px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265649" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0679-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0679-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0679.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265655" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0651-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0651-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0651.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265657" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0637-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0637-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0637.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>到今日（26 日）開場，SEGA 攤位亦正式開幕，裡面最大區域當然是《人中之龍 8 外傳 Pirates in Hawaii》試玩，即使今日是 TGS 商務日但現場排隊試玩的人龍，目視應該是全場數一數二最長！</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265629" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460283125_1309418937-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460283125_1309418937-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460283125_1309418937-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p>SEGA 今年在 TGS 裡面提供的《人中之龍 8 外傳 Pirates in Hawaii》試玩內容，由真島吾朗與諾亞在登陸夏威夷開始。在海灘上試玩真島的兩種戰鬥方式，狂犬 Style 與海盜 Style。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265641" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0023-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0023-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0023.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265642" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0027-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0027-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0027.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>狂犬 Style 利用了真島最在行的速度戰鬥，以拳腳、小刀攻擊，另外打擊敵人飛天後，可跳上空中漂浮對敵人施展追擊，在空中展開不同技法。在這個 Style 裡面可儲「狂氣計」，儲滿後可發動「分身」攻擊，在分身途中真島本人更可施展回轉攻擊等特殊技。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265638" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0014-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0014-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0014.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265637" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0022-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0022-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0022.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265643" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0016-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0016-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0016.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>海盜 Style 則是攻擊範圍廣闊的攻擊，真島可用上 3 種不同的海賊道具「手槍」「回力鏢」「二刀流刀劍」，切換這些道具進行近接、遠隔打擊。當然海盜 Style 也可滯空進行追擊。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265639" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0010-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0010-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0010.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265633" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0004-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0004-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0004.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265634" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0007-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0007-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0007.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在現場也可試玩最新遊戲熱點，包括卡拉 OK、瘋狂送外賣、龍賽車，還有換裝等等。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265640" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0029-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0029-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0029.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265630" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0028-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0028-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0028.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265632" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0003-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0003-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0003.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265631" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0002-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0002-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0002.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>試玩版還包括了登陸瘋狂蘭提斯的情景。今次試玩報道到此，期待日後 SEGA 有更多新資料公開。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265636" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0026-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0026-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0026.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265635" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0019-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0019-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0019.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265659" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0719-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0719-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0719.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/26/sega-tgs/game-channel/">【TGS 2024】SEGA TGS 派對美女如雲  《人中之龍 8 外傳》試玩</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
